    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es eſmu nahzistam KUN-\nGAM uppureht/ un tew buhs\nIsajn pee to Uppuri aizinaht/tad\ndohſchn es tew Sinzu/ ko tew\nbuhs darriht/ un tew buhs mán\n fwaidiht/ ko es tew fazzischu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Samuels darrija/ ko\ntas KUNGS bij runnajs/ un\nnahze uhs Betleini/ tad gabje ta\nPilssahta Wezzajee drebbedami\nwixnam pretti/ un fazzija: Woj\ntu ar Meeru nahz?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch fazzija: Ar Meer-\nru/ es eſmu nahzis tam KUN-\nGAM uppureht/ fwehttijeetees/\nun nahzeet ar mannim pee to Up-\npuri: Un wiꞥſch fwehtija Isaju\nun wixxa Dehlus/ un aizinaja\ntohs pee to Uppuri.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Rad tee nu nahze/ usluhko-\nja wiꞥſch Eliabu/ un dohmaja/\njaſchu tchis irr preeſch ta KUN-\nGA wixxa Swaidihts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet tas KUNGS fazzija\nus Samueu: Ne usluhko wix-\nna Gihwit/ nedg wixxa leelu\nGaxrumu/ jo es eſmu wixnu at-\nmettis. Jo tas ta ne irr ka Zil-\nweki reds/ Jo weens Zilweks reds/\nkas preeſch Azzim irr/ bet tas\nKUNGS usluhko to Sirdi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad aizinaja Isajus to A-\nbinadabu/ un likke to preeſch\nSamuelu eet/ bet wiꞥſch fazzija:\nIr scho tasKUNGS ne irr tsredsejs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad likke Isajus Samu-\npreckscha nahkt: Bet wiꞥſch fa-\nzija: Ir tcho tas KUNGS ne i\nisredsejs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tá likke Isajus fau-\nfeptians Dehlus preeksch Samu-\nelu nahkt/ bet Samuels fazzij\nus Isaju: Tas KUNGS ne i\nne weenu no fscheem fsredseje.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Attak fazzija Samuel\nuhs Isaju: Ar fchee irr wiﬀi te\nJaunefti? tas fazzija: tas jau\nnakajs wehl atleek/ un raugi\nwiꞥſch ganna tahs Awis. Ta-\nfazzija Samuels us Isaju; Sub-\nti us turren/ un dabbn win-\nschurp/ jo mehg ue apfchdefimees\nteekungs wiꞥſch buhs atnahzis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fuhttija wiꞥſch/ u\natwedde to/ ( nn tas btja pasar\nkans ar skaistahn Azzim/ un a\njauku Gihmi/) tad fazzija ta-\nKUNGS: Zellees/ un fwaid-\nto/ jo fchis irr tas pats.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nehme Samuels fa-\nwu Efjes-Diaggu/ un fwaidij-\nwixnu wixxa Brahtu Starpâ\nUn ta KUNGA Gars nahze pah-\nDahwidu tai Deená/ un we-\njoprohjam. Un Samuelszehlehs\nun nogahje uhs Rahmatu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ta KUNGA Gars\natkabpe no Saula/ un ween-\ntauns Gars beedinaja wixnu n-\nta KUNGA.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Saula Kalp-\nus to: Raugi jelle/ weens taun-\nGars no Deewa tew beedina.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Sakti jelle muhfu Kung-\nus taiweem Kalpeem/ fas preeſch-\n"
    }
  ],
